            <title>[LU-9762] Remove lsm_lock</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9762</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The lsm lock was formerly used to protect the lov_stripe_md struct.  That use has been replaced by the coh_attr_guard lock.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, we should remove it.  (This reduces the cost of lov_attr_get enough to be measurable in the tiny writes patch, &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/27903/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/27903/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
